name: Inspection Test Plan_MSB 4-4
Measurements and location of array marked in accordance with drawings
Panel clamps are installed properly and straight
Num. of rails match prescribed structural mounting zones
Rail overhang from last roof fixing does not exceed 500mm
Every row is earthed
Solar modules are installed square
Modules are max. 350mm from last fixing
Solar modules are correctly connected according the string configuration
Cables are installed neatly and without slack
Channels or cable trays used on the roof are earthed
Check MC4 connectors: termination and brand of connectors
Suitable cable management is installed on the roof
Penetration(s) done are properly sealed with silicone or fire-resistant foam (if required)
Inverters are mounted and installed correctly
Test equipotential bonding of frames and exposed conductive parts
Test string voltage, insulation resistance, polarity
All DC Cable is Mechanically protected
Protection board is installed and terminated correctly
Data cables correctly connected and terminated
Test inverter insulation resistance, continuity
Inverters connected to the data switch via cat 6.
Inverters are configured via app and online
All the components are labelled clearly
Foot Spacing Check Form
Maximum Allowed Spacing (mm) 1200 (on purlin), Spacing less than max
